  "body": "### description\r\n\r\nCurrently when we build the Docker images in CI the images are built with the entire repo as `context`\r\n\r\nThis means that for every build the entire repo is sent to the docker daemon.\r\n\r\nThis will slow down the build a lot, and may be related to the disk space issues in the CI build machine",
